Worth every penny.             https://www.coppercustom.com/shop/parts-kits/pantheon-arms-dolos-gen-2-kit-7-slotted-handguard/             MSRP $200

Law Tactical Folding Buttstock Adaptor. Fits with any buffer tube. Easy assembly. In this case its already installed.        http://www.brownells.com/rifle-parts/stock-parts/buttstocks/ar-15-m16-gen3-m-folding-stock-adapter-prod71553.aspx           MSRP $269
